ing:</b>\r\n<a title="Online Booking" href="http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/booking/">Bestil din vaccination nu!</a>\r\n</div>\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:6;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:7:"Genveje";s:4:"text";s:407:"• <a title="Online Booking" href="http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/booking/">Bestil tid til vaccination</a>\r\n• <a title="Webshop" href="http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/webshop/">Køb rejseartikler</a>\r\n• <a title="Vaccinationsanbefaling" href="http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/vaccinationsanbefaling/">Vaccineanbefalinger</a>\r\n• <a title="FAQ" href="http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/faq/">Ofte stillede spørgsmål</a>";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:7;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:130:"<img src="http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/logo-footer-gray.png" alt="DLVS" style="margin: 30px 50% 0 50%"/>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
