(2298, 1, '2012-01-12 12:24:47', '2012-01-12 12:24:47', 'Below are suggestions for medication you might wish to bring along on the trip. For further advice please read more under the specific sections.\r\n\r\nTravel advice - drugs on the trip:\r\n\r\n* Allergy: Anti-histamine tablets and antihistamine tablets.\r\n* Diarrhea: Antibiotics (ciprofloxacin or azithromycin), stopping over the counter medications and letters containing powder for rehydreringsvæske.\r\n* Heartburn: Acid Derogatory medication, available in both prescription and OTC drugs.\r\n* Altitude Sickness: Diamox.\r\n* Malaria: Bring the medication you have been prescribed by your doctor. Remember insect repellent.\r\n* Pain: Bring your regular painkillers over the counter medications.\r\n* Shuttle Sick: Antihistamines for motion sickness or skopolaminplastre.', 'Travel pharmacy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1082-revision-5', '', '', '2012-01-12 12:24:47', '2012-01-12 12:24:47', '', 1082, 'http://dlvsdk.konscript.net/1082-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
