(1725, 2, '2012-02-13 13:24:19', '2012-02-13 13:24:19', '<a href="http://travelvaccination.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/stockxpertcom_id30568_jpg_f9826905a4f831a43ad78dd3e3958522.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-1180" title="vaccination " src="http://travelvaccination.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/stockxpertcom_id30568_jpg_f9826905a4f831a43ad78dd3e3958522-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="1095" height="199" /></a>\r\n\r\nGoing travelling should be equal to a number of good experiences, but the good times may be overshadowed by illness and accidents. Fortunately, the vast majority of illnesses and accidents can be avoided if you just take some precautions.\r\n\r\nThis page tells you about these precautions.\r\n\r\nUnder each topic, there are facts about the disease and some practical advice you should follow before and during your trip.\r\n\r\nWe hope you have a great trip!', 'Travel Advice', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '413-revision-10', '', '', '2012-02-13 13:24:19', '2012-02-13 13:24:19', '', 413, 'http://travelvaccination.co.uk/413-revision-10/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
